the digital world and physical stores the companys omnichannel services including orderinstore reserveinstore findinstore and shipfromstore that are tailored across its portfolio of brands the company also sells products that are designed and manufactured by branded thirdparties especially at its intermix brands gap inc has companyoperated stores in the united states canada the united kingdom france ireland japan italy china hong kong taiwan and mexico it operates gap banana republic and old navy stores throughout asia australia europe latin america the middle east and africagapgap is the apparel and accessories brands anchored in optimistic casual american style its collections of wardrobes include denim tees buttondowns and khakis gap includes apparel and accessories for men and women under the name gap name in addition to gapkids babygap gapmaternity gapbody and gapfit collections gap serves through specialty stores online and franchise stores gap also offers a suite of omnichannel services to its customers in the united states in addition it brings the brand to customers with designer collections for gap outlet and gap factory stores and websitesbanana republicbanana republic is an apparel and accessories brand focused on delivering versatile contemporary classics customers can purchase banana republic products in its specialty and outlet stores online and in franchise storesold navyold navy is an apparel and accessories brand customers can purchase old navy products in companyoperated and franchise stores and onlineathletaathleta is a fitness and lifestyle brand creating performance apparel for women and girls athleta integrates technical features and design across its womens collection such as motion from yoga training and sports to everyday activities and travel customers can purchase athleta products in the united states through its stores and catalogs or through its websiteintermixintermix curates musthave styles from the designers intermix delivers a point of view and an individualized approach to shopping and personal style customers can shop in stores in the united states and canada and onlineweddington wayweddington way is a social shopping platform for wedding parties featuring an online boutique with bridesmaid dresses and a curated selection of wedding party gifts customers can shop weddington way online and the brand ships globally » full overview of gps company address gap inc  folsom stsan francisco   ca    p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation robert fisher  jeff kirwan  arthur peck  teri liststoll  mark breitbard  » more officers  directors gap inc news rptfashion ma like a crop top is hard to pull off jul   fashion ma like a crop top is hard to pull off jul   refilefashion ma like a crop top is hard to pull off jul   debtladen neiman marcus abandons hope of a sale jun   upscale retailer neiman marcus posts th straight quarterly loss jun   » more gps news related topics stocksstock screenerapparel  accessories retailers product marketing skip navigation gap inc careers mobile menu search search keyword location radius radius  miles  miles  miles  miles  miles search product  marketingcareer areas be a brandbuilder these teams create great designs turn them into musthave products make plans for selling them and tells the world about them creative types analytical types types who combine the best of both…there’s a place for every type of talent here what matters is that you’re curious inventive collaborative and aren’t satisfied with the status quo marketing perfect fit for the creative problemsolver if you join our marketing team you’ll have one of the most exciting gigs in retail helping to draw the roadmap for our global brands through a variety of landscapes from ad campaigns to media relations to instore and digital campaigns to tell each brand’s unique story in ways that connect with customers and drive their awareness of what’s happening in each new season you’ll collaborate with internal teams and external creatives — zeroing in on the right messages and delivering them in fun surprising and effective ways that drive sales build brand loyalty and strengthen our reputation example marketing roles assistant marketing manager online promotions art director marketing manager email  promotions senior manager lifecycle marketing – global consumer payments view all marketing jobs design perfect fit for fashion obsessives if you join our design team you’ll draw on equal parts trend and inspiration to bring bold ideas to life build collections that customers love and watch your work define fashion on millions of people around the world with amazing opportunities across all five gap inc brands our designers get handson experience with everything from luxury lines to valueoriented design for all “i think there are a lot of companies where you don’t get to have your sense and your say when you’re designing gap is a place where you really do get to be influential and creative” – satya women‘s design director at gap example design roles associate designer designer textile designer view all design jobs meet our designers  want to join our team check out opportunities at all five of our brands — gap banana republic old navy athleta and intermix visit gapinccomcareers merchandising perfect fit for those who love the big picture if you join our merchandising team you’ll be a brand manager a customer champion and a driver of sales merchants are the backbone of the product development process driving assortment strategies across brands channels and countries you’ll use consumer insights market data and information about our business performance to surprise and excite customers with the great product you bring to market online and in stores and you’ll use every part of your brain because you’ll move constantly and fluidly between highlevel strategic thinking and tactical execution merchants are forever curious and always looking to find new ways to see and interpret the big picture across categories channels and brands example merchandising roles merchandising assistant merchandiser merchandiser merchandiser licensing divisional merchandise manager view all merchandising jobs meet our merchandising team  want to join our team check out opportunities at all five of our brands — gap banana republic old navy athleta and intermix visit gapinccomcareers inventory management and planning perfect fit for the strategically savvy if you join our inventory management team you’ll use your business and financial skills to create execute and communicate the strategies that boost our bottom line you’ll come up with innovative ways to meet and exceed sales and margin goals and will manage product sales and inventory plans through forecasting allocation and supply chain operations example inventory management and planning roles inventory planning or allocation analyst inventor planner senior inventory planner view all inventory jobs meet our inventory management team  want to join our team check out opportunities at all five of our brands — gap banana republic old navy athleta and intermix visit gapinccomcareers production perfect fit for the collaborative type if you join our production team you’ll work closely with designers merchants and vendors to understand the latest trends and redefine them for our brands — not only turning initial sketches into beautiful wellmade pieces at the right cost and in the right quantities but also making sure they get to our warehouses and stores on time youll be laserfocused on fit technical design and quality and even help test products and solve quality issues to make sure everything we sell is the best in its category example production roles associate production manager production manager technical designer view all production jobs meet our production team  want to join our team check out opportunities at all five of our brands — gap banana republic old navy athleta and intermix visit g